Package: actulife
Type: Package
Title: Life insurence calculations classes and functions
LazyData: true
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2017-08-26
Author: Oskar Laverny <oskar.laverny@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Oskar Laverny <oskar.laverny@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains classes for life table and actuarial life tables, dicrete or continuous cases, and a lot of function to perform life insurence calculations with them : expectations and probabilities, but also Insurences, anuities (due or immediate), inter-ages assumptions (UDD, CFM), group at first death, group at last death, group at Kth death and any group using Schuett-Nesbitt, Reserving, etc.
    A few usual life tables are provied as data (mainly french ones) to perform tests.
